  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Float>, java.util.Collection<java.lang.Float>, java.util.List<java.lang.Float>, java.util.RandomAccess, ConstProperties, DebuggableObject, ExternalArrayData, IdFunctionCall, Scriptable

    public class NativeFloat32Array
extends NativeTypedArrayView<java.lang.Float>
    An array view that stores 32-bit quantities and implements the JavaScript "loat32Array" interface. It also implements List for direct manipulation in Java.
